title: Hong Kong Style Bubble Waffles (no music version, not tutorial)
description:
My first attempt at making Hong Kong Style Egg or Bubble Waffles!

I followed this exactly, with the exception of substituting custard powder with instant vanilla pudding mix (Jell-O brand), and vanilla essence with vanilla extract.

The bubble waffle maker I used was the CucinaPro Bubble Waffle Maker.

Editor: VSDC Video Editor
